summary: Helpert (Thailand) Co., Ltd. has entered into a lease agreement dated July 23, 2025, for office space on the 24th floor of 66 Tower, totaling 488.0 square meters, with a three-year lease term starting September 1, 2025. The monthly rent and service fee is 650.00 Thai Baht per square meter, with additional costs for parking, utilities, and other services. The tenant must pay a deposit and comply with building regulations and standards for renovations and use of the space.
